When The SHTF - SURVIVAL for 2014 Vol 15 - 717 Encyclopedias Of Everything - Mega Pack



When The Spit Hits The Fan




Comment: When the Time comes to Head for The Hills. You need to be ready to leave town with everything you need in 10 minutes. Once you get out of town THEN you have to Survive!!! Here are some good Survival Tips.

Description:

There are over 700 Encyclopedias in this collection. When the net goes down, you will still have the info you need in this collection.
